to your gut.

336
00:20:33.357 --> 00:20:34.483 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I think it's right.

337
00:20:34.566 --> 00:20:36.360 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
I'm positive it is!

338
00:20:36.443 --> 00:20:40.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Though when it comes to me,
"gut" has another meaning.

339
00:20:40.530 --> 00:20:43.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
You're right,
but we've got trouble coming.

340
00:20:43.742 --> 00:20:46.078 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
We have to do something.

341
00:20:46.161 --> 00:20:47.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
[Mario]
"I shall faithfully uphold

342
00:20:47.704 --> 00:20:49.831 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the constitution
of the Kingdom of Cremona

343
00:20:49.915 --> 00:20:52.626 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
and comply with all orders
decreed by our king.

344
00:20:52.709 --> 00:20:54.628 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
I shall place them
before my duties

345
00:20:54.711 --> 00:20:57.756 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
as an officer of the law
and demand they be obeyed."

346
00:20:58.799 --> 00:21:01.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
"And with favor toward none
and with fear toward nothing,

347
00:21:02.010 --> 00:21:03.595 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
without malice or ill will,

348
00:21:03.679 --> 00:21:05.138 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
obeying only
my inner conscience..."

349
00:21:06.473 --> 00:21:07.933 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
"...to safeguard the kingdom,

350
00:21:08.016 --> 00:21:11.061 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
as well as the freedom and
rights of all her citizens,

351
00:21:11.144 --> 00:21:13.480 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
