to carry out my duties

352
00:21:13.563 --> 00:21:15.399 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
as an officer of the law!"

353
00:21:15.482 --> 00:21:18.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<i>-♪ Someday I'll be gone... ♪</i>
-The day we took that oath,

354
00:21:18.944 --> 00:21:22.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
the three of us became cops,
and damn good ones.

355
00:21:22.698 --> 00:21:26.618 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
We just have to keep
solving cases one after another.

356
00:21:26.702 --> 00:21:29.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Honestly, that's all we can do.

357
00:21:30.622 --> 00:21:32.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
But, as small as they are,

358
00:21:32.374 --> 00:21:33.834 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
as those victories add up,

359
00:21:33.917 --> 00:21:35.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
they'll eventually
grow into a clue

360
00:21:35.711 --> 00:21:38.630 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
that will hopefully lead us
right to a breakthrough,

361
00:21:38.714 --> 00:21:41.216 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
'cause that's what I think.

362
00:21:41.300 --> 00:21:44.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
And having said all of that,
I still have no earthly idea

363
00:21:44.720 --> 00:21:47.055 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
when that breakthrough
is gonna happen for us.

364
00:21:48.140 --> 00:21:49.433 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
You're right.

365
00:21:49.516 --> 00:21:52.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
Therefore, thinking
about all that other stuff

