00:21:57.983 --> 00:21:59.401 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
Yeah, I get it.

368
00:21:59.484 --> 00:22:02.738 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
From now on,
I won't think anymore!

