<i>♪ Cursing shadows ♪</i>

371
00:22:13.290 --> 00:22:15.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>♪ Hunt and gather ♪</i>

372
00:22:15.375 --> 00:22:19.254 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<i>♪ In the city of no answer ♪</i>

